data.description: HUGE PRICE REDUCTION - PRICED TO SELL. You will love this bright and neutral tone split bedroom floor plan pool home located in the Port Charlotte Sec 015 neighborhood. Great home for entertaining family and friends. The kitchen has wood cabinets, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, breakfast counter and pantry storage closet. Relax in the large informal eating area is open to the kitchen and family room; all offering cathedral ceilings. The formal dining room and front living room/sitting area have high ceilings and provide additional entertaining areas.  The primary bedroom has high ceilings, private en suite bathroom, his and her walk-in closet and sliding glass door to the lanai and pool areas. The other two bedrooms have a private hallway with a pocket door, walk-in closet and a full bathroom with access to the pool area.  The rear screened in lanai with inground pool has views of the private garden between the pool cage and the tall wooden privacy fence.  The wooden fenced (2023) rear yard, pool and garden is the oasis you've been waiting for. The garage has a wall air conditioning unit. Newer roof in 2022. Additional features include some hurricane impact windows, newer soffits and gutters, newer cage screening, 6’ x 8’ garden storage shed, well irrigation, paver driveway and front porch, all bathrooms feature granite counters plus an interior spacious laundry room. Fantastic location close to great schools, easy access to I-75, restaurants, shopping, golf, fishing, boating and just a short drive to Charlotte Harbor, downtown historic Punta Gorda and SWFL gulf beaches. Don’t miss this opportunity to call this home!
